snippet.title: Gift Wrapped (Nitrome.com) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay of Gift Wrapped. A Nitrome christmas minigame about finding the maximum number of gifts in a short time.
You can play it in: http://www.nitrome.com/games/giftwrapped/?game=giftwrapped#.X4NEvuf45PY
I hope you like it!
